					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13575178#post-4726794</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13575178/scp-5512#post-4726794</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2020 02:07:35 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>There never was such a thing as absolute justice, but only agreements made in mutual dealings among men in whatever places at various times providing against the infliction or suffering of harm.<br /> - <strong>Epicurus</strong>, <em>Principal Doctrines</em></p> </blockquote> <p>Well, here is the often rewritten and finally uploaded follow up to <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4612">SCP-4612</a>. Taken me the better part of 3 months to figure this out and I hope y’all like it.</p> <p>This is a story about a man (sorta) who is very much alone and embittered against all of society for good reason, and instead of merely accepting his lot or taking up some ill-advised campaign of revenge, decides to make a society of his own. More importantly, it is about the hurdles one might face in creating a society all by one’s lonesome.</p> <p>If you are interested in my other works: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/grigori-karpin-s-author-page">Grigori Karpin's Author Page</a></p> <p>Also, it's probably obvious, but this article follows from <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4612">SCP-4612</a></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">►&nbsp;Spoilers&nbsp;◄</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;ok,&nbsp;you&nbsp;asked&nbsp;for&nbsp;it:&nbsp;▼</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>• Diego Marquez is a false identity and he has had contact with Dr. Iona Varga and the personnel of Site-91 before.<br /> • Marquez is genuinely concerned for his congregation and wants to help them become more like him… but doesn’t quite see the disconnect between that caring and the results of his experiments.<br /> • The entity which is seen towards the end of the article is the same species as the cadaver found in SCP-4612.<br /> • Moreover, the entity and Marquez are NOT reality benders in anyway. They are operating under a system of thaumaturgy that has been hardwired into reality and doesn’t require rituals.<br /> • This isn’t the last we’ll be seeing of these cultists or Mr. Marquez.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Critique</span></strong>:<br /> Help: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magic8ball04" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5529621&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Magic8Ball04" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5529621)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/magic8ball04" >Magic8Ball04</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5986843&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Ralliston" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5986843)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ralliston" >Ralliston</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/charvel" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5424447&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Charvel" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5424447)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/charvel" >Charvel</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-whitney" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5252186&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Dr Whitney" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5252186)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-whitney" >Dr Whitney</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" >stormbreath</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span><br /> In-depth Critque: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1777811&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="weizhong" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1777811)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weizhong" >weizhong</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" >cybersqyd</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4665703&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="Nagiros" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4665703)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" >Nagiros</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mountaintimepunch" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2028454&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998788" alt="MountainTimePunch" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2028454)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mountaintimepunch" >MountainTimePunch</a></span></p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/hecatoncheires-cycle-hub">Hecatoncheires Cycle</a></strong></p> </div> 
